    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Today, these mechanical constructs are considered the last remnants of ancient civilisation. Created thousands of years ago to serve as tools or guardians of knowledge, the abilities of one Autarch can hardly be compared with those of another. They all harbour a connection between long-forgotten technology and powerful magic. Their bodies are forged from different metals.</p><p>The Delta Kilo series differs from the other Autarchs in many ways. They are humanoid in shape and were (it is assumed) created for social purposes. They have a highly developed artificial intelligence and the ability to copy and accurately reflect different emotions.</p><h3>Delta Kilo Traits</h3><p><strong>Creature Type:</strong> Construct</p><p><strong>Size:</strong> Medium (80-160cm)</p><p><strong>Speed:</strong> 30 ft. walking, 10 ft. climbing, 10 ft. swimming (unable to truly swim; walks along the bottom of bodies of water)</p><p>As a Delta Kilo Autarch, you have these special traits.</p>",
